<refnamediv><refname>imvideocapabilities</refname><refpurpose>Report exposed video and camera capabilities.</refpurpose></refnamediv>
<refsynopsisdiv><title>Syntax</title><synopsis>capabilities = imvideocapabilities()</synopsis></refsynopsisdiv>
<refsection><title>Description</title><para><function>imvideocapabilities</function> reports whether video read/write, camera read, and property get/set wrappers are exposed in this build.</para></refsection>
<refsection><title>Examples</title><programlisting role="example"><![CDATA[
capabilities = imvideocapabilities();
disp(capabilities.propertyGetSet);
]]></programlisting></refsection>
